{"tid":987570,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"熊二? 28000? 定只係反彈浪?","createTime":"2019-01-19T12:01:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-19T17:04:53.000Z","uid":177039,"like":10,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"85b7e34413dd51035c2a0ba1697ac3ce72f63783","tid":987570,"uid":177039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T12:01:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xBaSQa8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxBaSQa8.jpg&h=48149650&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n18/1 恒指向上突破270 從PVT當中可見放量(已經超過左12月反彈浪頂既數目),近幾日成交量亦見增加 升多幾百點應該冇問題<br />\n但問題係真係B浪定係反彈浪呢?<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E9CFeCZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE9CFeCZ.jpg&h=7d7f63d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n從數浪角度呢一下個人睇法有機會只係A4-3反彈浪  假設 A4-1 同 A4-3既升幅大致相同<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/up4PSsH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fup4PSsH.jpg&h=8f62de28&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n咁A4-1升左大慨2670點 而A4-3由24896開始升到大約275-276就會係浪頂<br />\n配合返我個人數浪睇法A1大浪底部係27714 (配合四浪不入一浪底原則) 再加上黃金比A3浪頂底(28579 - 24540) 0.764既反彈位就會係27625<br />\n分析得出既野都令我懷疑B浪既可能性<br />\n<br />\n<strong>但最後都要問返自己一句, 你覺得而家既基本因素/政策既改變有冇足夠能力令股市行一個熊二呢?</strong><br />\n利申個人意見 講錯唔好插咁大力<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0c668876da62232da2db734867cf018c12a7cc1","tid":987570,"uid":59014,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T12:04:38.000Z","msg":"熊三完左 24000係底<br />\n而加牛一 好大機會慢升去29000"},{"pid":"c0073c51ab33aca231cbb46e7ce2714624871362","tid":987570,"uid":45440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"85b7e34413dd51035c2a0ba1697ac3ce72f63783","tid":987570,"uid":177039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-19T12:01:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xBaSQa8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxBaSQa8.jpg&h=48149650&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n18/1 恒指向上突破270 從PVT當中可見放量(已